(7.8 +/- 4.8 years) and duration of follow-up (8.8 +/- 4.8 years) were similar. 
Therapeutic modalities in the two groups were also similar. Of group I patients, 
78% (42/54) reached ESRD compared with 33% (4/12) of group II patients (P less 
than 0.01). Life table analysis showed that 50% of black and Hispanic children 
will reach ESRD within 3 years of FSGS.(ABSTRACT TRUNCATED AT 250 WORDS)

